<item>
            <title>[CASSANDRA-6213] Updating Pig to 0.11.1 breaks the existing Pig driver</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CASSANDRA-6213</link>
                <project id="12310865" key="CASSANDRA">Apache Cassandra</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Current trunk upgrades Pig to 0.11.1 which causes the Pig storages code can&apos;t compile. Pig storages need implement the new API method cleanupOnSuccess(String,Job).&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="12674372">CASSANDRA-6213</key>
            <summary>Updating Pig to 0.11.1 breaks the existing Pig driver</summary>
