                                                                                                                <comments>
                            <comment id="13798272" author="alexliu68" created="Thu, 17 Oct 2013 18:56:18 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Fixed compiling error in trunk&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13798289" author="brandon.williams" created="Thu, 17 Oct 2013 19:06:19 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Committed&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13864070" author="jeromatron" created="Tue, 7 Jan 2014 10:28:05 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=alexliu68&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;alexliu68&quot;&gt;alexliu68&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=brandon.williams&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;brandon.williams&quot;&gt;brandon.williams&lt;/a&gt; Is there a reason this can&apos;t get merged into 2.0 so that 2.0 can use Pig 0.11.1 and 0.12.0?&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13864259" author="brandon.williams" created="Tue, 7 Jan 2014 14:25:04 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;We aren&apos;t going to change a lib version in a minor release.  We could backport this, but since we build with pig you&apos;d have to roll your own custom release to use 0.11 or 0.12.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13864281" author="jeromatron" created="Tue, 7 Jan 2014 14:42:47 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;ok.  unfortunate but makes sense since we&apos;ve had issues with updating dependency libs in a minor release in the past.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13864303" author="jeromatron" created="Tue, 7 Jan 2014 14:52:21 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Can we update our dependency to 0.12 so that we&apos;re current with the pig stable releases before 2.1 is released?&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13864320" author="jeromatron" created="Tue, 7 Jan 2014 15:09:17 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I created a separate ticket so we can revisit upgrading before going to beta with 2.1: &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CASSANDRA-6556&quot; title=&quot;Update Pig dependency to latest stable before releasing 2.1&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;CASSANDRA-6556&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;CASSANDRA-6556&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
